  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 5 flow-speed combinations. Thirteen credibility factors are assessed. The package carries a rebutting defeater: the Model Form factor achievedLevel (2) falls one step below its requiredLevel (3), yet the hasDecisionRecord outcome is Accepted.",
